schools.name: Judith A Resnik Community Learning Center

data.description: Location, location, location! This gorgeous 4 bdrm, 3 bath home is nestled in one of Akron's MOST BEAUTIFUL neighborhoods; Fairlawn Heights. As you drive in you'll immediately appreciate your surroundings, the quiet feel, the mature trees, yet SO close to all amenities. This home offers a wonderful layout with ample living space between the front living room with picture window and the cozy back family room with wood burning fireplace and sliding door to the gorgeous and private back yard. The roomy eat-in kitchen is at the heart of the home and opens to the formal dining room and sunken family room making this a dream home for entertaining. There is also a large bedroom and half bath to add even more convenience to this home. Upstairs you'll find a master en suite with walk in shower, and 2 additional large bedrooms and another full bath. There is a full basement just waiting to be finished off for even more space.
